{"tid":2039410,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【抗暴之戰】曾參與聯署聲明反送中 報道指高等法院法官李瀚良需停審反修例案件","createTime":"2020-05-28T04:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T04:15:44.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61ec1e7d7466f5c75e40d7ff3187b848ff27835d","tid":2039410,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:10:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200528/F7COVYEPGLKTKY3FOIPULQTWDA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200528%2FF7COVYEPGLKTKY3FOIPULQTWDA%2F&d=%2FAUJPsyZ5YTgQdLV7Kr5PkYD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=ad945c5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200528%2FF7COVYEPGLKTKY3FOIPULQTWDA%2F&h=63cc0059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200528/F7COVYEPGLKTKY3FOIPULQTWDA/</a><br />\n<br />\n高等法院原訟法庭法官李瀚良去年在6.9遊行前夕，與港大逾3千校友在報章刊登題為《反對謊言施政 撤回引渡惡法》聯署聲明，事後司法機構承認有法官參與是次聯署，又指終審法院首席法官馬道立曾與該法官討論，並提醒將來應避免同類事情發生。今日《星島日報》引述指，司法機構根據《法官行為指引》，在編排李瀚良審理的案件時，為避免出現「表面偏頗」的情況，李官需迴避處理與該聯署聲明有關議題的案件，即不許處理反修例案件。"},{"pid":"6290c274013a0912da1ed0d5304ef0a9be76435b","tid":2039410,"uid":124180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:11:10.000Z","msg":"咁搞法會唔會冇哂人番呢一年既案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb7a811f2acb5d7ed1dcc5e0d31cd17c58e0dc6","tid":2039410,"uid":94771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以制度內真係唔會夠仍玩<br />\n郭狗官做到咁撚出面先DQ 1個<br />\n人地就你簽個名都DQ正常法官<br />\n<br />\n人地就真係 撕一撕十"},{"pid":"176128261bd6928d758d40c96b6e3207b1c431b9","tid":2039410,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:12:41.000Z","msg":"藍色果班又唔見咁快手BAN佢地"},{"pid":"336197c78dc62201e91548a3e458aaaf5a451d99","tid":2039410,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi